wikipedia_page.main: Ryan Samir Patel (born 26 October 1997) is an English cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Surrey in the 2017 County Championship on 28 August 2017.In June 2018, during the 2018 County Championship match against Somerset, he took his maiden five-wicket haul in first-class cricket, with six wickets for five runs in eleven balls. He made his List A debut on 30 April 2019, for Surrey in the 2019 Royal London One-Day Cup. He made his Twenty20 debut on 26 July 2019, for Surrey in the 2019 t20 Blast.
